Reasoning: The paper deals with constraint satisfaction problems for templates over the integers, which involves discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The use of homomorphisms and polymorphisms suggests a connection to logic and model theory, which falls under cs.LO. The study of CSPs also has applications in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS).
